<subSubSection id="616AE25AD8A3259730F9A355335BBBAB" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="AF34432C1B93CB03A58DE117DC71C62C" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A42535E03CCC69CBF4AE707DB498B741" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">
Medium sized (10.3 mm), bluish species (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="A2FAEDB2AC82E7F62C5A239E1F31A018" captionStart="Figure 29" captionStartId="F29" captionText="Figure 29. Merodon nigropunctum sp. nov., male. A body, dorsal view B body, lateral view C left wing, dorsal view. Scale bar: 2 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.909.46838.figure29" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/377390" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">29A, B</figureCitation>
) with dark macula on medial part of wing (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="45B3934D4E1EB584F201E4DD94E91866" captionStart="Figure 29" captionStartId="F29" captionText="Figure 29. Merodon nigropunctum sp. nov., male. A body, dorsal view B body, lateral view C left wing, dorsal view. Scale bar: 2 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.909.46838.figure29" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/377390" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">29C</figureCitation>
); basoflagellomere narrow and elongated, 1.8 times as long as wide, rounded at the tip (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="6C268A507531549DD999F24BA51767A0" captionStart="Figure 28" captionStartId="F28" captionText="Figure 28. Antenna. A Merodon nigropunctum sp. nov., outer side lateral view, male B Merodon nigropunctum sp. nov., inner side, lateral view, male C Merodon nigrocapillatus sp. nov., outer side, lateral view, male D Merodon nigrocapillatus sp. nov., outer side, lateral view, female. Scale bar: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.909.46838.figure28" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/377389" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">28A, B</figureCitation>
); arista long, two times as long as basoflagellomere; body pile whitish; posterior half of scutum with square shaped area of black pile medially; terga 2-4 covered with black pile medially, except whitish pilosity on conspicuous silver microtrichose fasciae (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="5420CAE09B6354EC29426D71D885AC89" captionStart="Figure 29" captionStartId="F29" captionText="Figure 29. Merodon nigropunctum sp. nov., male. A body, dorsal view B body, lateral view C left wing, dorsal view. Scale bar: 2 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.909.46838.figure29" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/377390" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">29A</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption id="18A35F1CA9F4EB691183E7EC3D20A407" doi="10.3897/zookeys.909.46838.figure29" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/377390" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" start="Figure 29" startId="F29">
